Privacy Policy
Introduction
We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information when you use our website, products, and apps.
1. Information We Collect
1.1. Information You Provide
We collect information that you voluntarily provide when you use our website or apps, including:
Personal Information:
Name, email address, phone number, and other contact details.
Account Information:
Username, password, and profile information.
Payment Information:
Credit card details and billing information when you make a purchase.
Communications:
Any messages or inquiries you send to us.
1.2. Information We Collect Automatically
When you use our website or apps, we automatically collect certain information, including:
Usage Information:
Pages or features accessed, time spent on the site or app, and interaction data.
Device Information:
IP address, browser type, operating system, and device identifiers.
Cookies and Tracking Technologies:
Cookies, web beacons, and similar technologies to track user activity and preferences.
1.3. Information from Third Parties
We may receive information about you from third parties, such as social media platforms, if you use these services to log in or interact with our website or apps.
2. How We Use Your Information
We use the information we collect to:
Provide and Improve Services:
Deliver, maintain, and improve our website, products, and apps.
Personalize Experience:
Customize content and recommendations based on your preferences.
Communicate with You:
Respond to inquiries, send updates, and provide customer support.
Process Transactions:
Facilitate payments and manage orders.
Analyze Usage:
Monitor and analyze trends, usage, and activities to improve our services.
Marketing:
Send promotional materials and updates, with your consent where required by law.
Compliance:
Comply with legal obligations and protect our rights and interests.
3. How We Share Your Information
We may share your information with:
Service Providers:
Third-party vendors who perform services on our behalf, such as payment processing, data analysis, and marketing assistance.
Business Partners:
Partners we collaborate with to offer products or services.
Legal Requirements:
Authorities or other parties when required by law or to protect our rights and interests.
Corporate Transactions:
In connection with a merger, sale, or other business transfer.
4. Data Security
We implement security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no security system is impenetrable, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
5. Data Retention
We retain your information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law.
6. Your Choices
6.1. Access and Update
You can access and update your personal information by logging into your account or contacting us.
6.2. Opt-Out
You can opt-out of receiving promotional communications from us by following the unsubscribe instructions in the communications or contacting us directly.
6.3. Cookies
You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings. However, disabling cookies may affect your ability to use certain features of our website or apps.
7. Childrenâ€™s Privacy
Our website and apps are not intended for children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we become aware that we have collected such information, we will take steps to delete it.
8. International Transfers
Your information may be transferred to and processed in countries other than your own. We will take appropriate measures to ensure that your personal information remains protected.
9. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and we will notify you of significant changes. Your continued use of our website or apps after any changes indicates your acceptance of the revised policy.
10. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:
info@devnex.nl
By using our website or apps, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.